NOTES
The software currently has been tested only under GNU/Linux systems
However, binaries will be made available in the future

PREREQUISITES

For cytostream

    Python     - www.python.org
    PyQt4      - http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/software/pyqt/intr0
    Numpy      - http://numpy.scipy.org/
    Matplotlib - http://matplotlib.sourceforge.net/
    fcm        - http://code.google.com/p/py-fcm/

For fcm
    SciPy      - http://www.scipy.org/
    traits     - http://code.enthought.com/projects/traits/

ON MECURIAL

A good start for the .hginore file would be somthing like

*****************************
./*/projects/*
.*\.pyc
.*~
config_cs.py
./.hg/hgrc
./dist/*
./build/*
fcm.log

*****************************

hgrc file

*****************************
[paths]
default = https://<username>%%40gmail.com:<generated.passkey@cytostream.googlecode.com/hg/

[ui]
username = <username>@gmail.com

****************************
GETTING_STARTED

$ python setup.py install
$ python
> from cytostream import Main
> Main()

or
$ cd ~/.../cytostream/cytostream/
$ python Main.py

****************************